  "text": "NSD-1015. To measure the in vivo rate of dopamine biosynthesis, mice were injected intraperitoneally with 100 mg/kg NSD-1015 [CITATION_1] . The dorsal striata were dissected from animals killed 40 min after the injection, and the level of accumulated L-DOPA was determined by HPLC analysis as described below.",
